&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Perion is a global advertising technology company delivering solutions to the biggest brands and publishers around the globe across search, social media and display, video, CTV, and programmatic DOOH.&lt;/p&gt;
